App updated! Like that song, Faster Better Stronger!
Get the latest version which includes bug fixes and general improvements. 
Get more time back for the other good things in your life!

We bring updates regularly to make math learning and problem solving even easier for you!

We are also hoping you to send your advice to make our service even better, please get in touch at us: feedback@gauthmath.com

This is a BIG update for all students.

- A brand new look of Gauthmath.
- Enough tutors for all levels of math problems.
- Word problems and calculation, all you need is a simple snap!
- Team up with your friends, there will be a surprise for you!
- Step-by-step explanations upgraded, we know only answers are not enough.
